          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/449_step-6-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the potato wedges are nearly cooked, heat a dry, non-stick pan over a high heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>halloumi steaks</strong></p><p>Cook on each side for 1-2 min or until golden</p>",
